# ============================================================================
# NOTES
# ============================================================================
# 
# Order matters! Later matches override earlier ones.
# Use team slugs (@org/team-name) when working with GitHub Organizations.
# Use individual handles (@username) for personal repositories.
#
# Patterns:
# - * matches any string except /
# - ** matches any string including /
# - ? matches any single character
# - [abc] matches any character in the set
#
# Examples:
# /docs/**/*.md @doc-team
# *.js @javascript-team
# /apps/**/test/ @qa-team
#
# ============================================================================
